QUEEN GODDESS brushed an outer rival at the start, pressed two wide, but gave way between horses entering the lane.

NAPA CANDY lacked speed in the four path, fanned to the seven path entering the lane, and failed to factor. CURRENT CLIMATE laid off of the pace along the inside, and faded. AWESOME TREAT chased two wide, and weakened.
